room_title: Escape room "Nora's Nightmare" by Puzzling Escape in Phoenix
room_description: Nora is an imaginative little girl whose dreams have always been filled with unicorns and rainbows, but ever since her special dream catcher went missing, she has been having increasingly disturbing dreams. Now, little Nora is afraid to sleep in her own bedroom. Can you work together as a team to find out what is causing Nora’s nightmares and find her missing dream catcher– before it’s lights out?
